SAGA-DETR

This repository is derived from Salience-DETR:
https://github.com/xiuqhou/Salience-DETR

Salience-DETR is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0. The original
license text is preserved in LICENSE. Portions of the codebase, project
structure, model components, dataset utilities, transforms, training loop, and
documentation structure originate from Salience-DETR and are modified for the
SAGA-DETR research project.

SAGA-DETR additions include the VisDrone configuration and lightweight tools,
Assignment Certificate Margin Loss (ACML), Geometry-aware Structured Deformable
Attention (GSDA), and Boundary-Band Contrast Refinement (BBCR).

No datasets, checkpoints, pretrained weights, or generated experiment artifacts
are included in this release.
